रहीम के दोहे

Kah Rahim Kaise Nbhe Ber Ker Ko Sang
Vo dole Man Aapne Unke Faate Aang...

2 viprit Nature wale log ek saath kaise rah sakte hai...ek ke swabhavik gun se dosre ko haani ho sakti hai...jaise ber ke perh mein bahut kaante hote hai aur kale ka patte komal hote hai...bair ka perh mast hawa mein jhoomta hai...to kale ke patte kanto se chalni ho jaate hai...

Rahiman Dhaaga Prem Ka Mut Toro Chatkay
Jore Se Fir Na jure, Jure Gaanth Per Jaye...

Pyar ke Rishto mein khatas lnahi laani Chahiye...Ek Baar manmutav ho jata hai...to pahele jaise baat nahi raheti...jaise ager dhaaga toot jaye to jorne se usme gaanth zaroor aa jati hai...